name: GuessTheAnimal
0:
”Alexa, start Guess The Animal.”
”Alexa, open Guess The Animal.”
”That's a Dog.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: guess the animal
des: A fun game to teach animal sounds to kids during the early development stage. Helps with memory and kills boredom. Just start the skill, listen to the animal or bird sound and reply with its name. You can skip by saying 'Next' or repeat the old one by saying 'Previous' or repeat the existing one by saying 'Repeat'. To terminate and exit the game, say 'Stop'.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
